lead_paragraph: Clemson coach Dabo Swinney was ready to see his third-ranked Tigers build momentum for the final regular-season push. He couldn't be happier with their performance against Syracuse.

headline.print_headline: Watson Leads No. 3 Clemson to Blowout of 'Cuse Before Injury
